source: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_SEQ_00<tab>The tunnels are teeming with a few too many of Zo Ga's followers and flunkies for 789th Order Dustman Bo Bu's liking.
target: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_SEQ_00<tab>Im Abbaugebiet des 789. Ordens will Bo Bu für frische Luft sorgen (... lassen).

source: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_SEQ_01<tab>In Bo Bu's estimation, the blustering Zo Ga has assumed his lofty position not by his own merits, but by the nigh-fanatical support of a host of formidable followers. Make for U'Ghamaro and dispatch at least five of Zo Ga's elite─roundsmen, quarrymen, priests, or bedesmen─that the fugleman's iron grip on the tunnels might be weakened.
target: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_SEQ_01<tab>Bo Bu leidet unter dem fauligen Gestank, der aus den U'Ghamaro-Minen weht. Um für frische Luft zu sorgen, sollst du fünf beliebige Elite-Kobolde aus Zo Gas Gefolge besiegen. Dazu gehören <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F209D6030202 /var>, <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F209D7030202 /var>, <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F209D8030202 /var> und <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F209D9030202 /var>.

source: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_SEQ_02<tab>Five of Zo Ga's minions have fallen by your hand, realizing too late the fate of those that cast their lot with would-be tyrants. Return to the 789th Order Dig and share news of your triumph with Bo Bu.
target: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_SEQ_02<tab>Du hast Zo Gas Gefolge ordentlich dezimiert. Sage Bo Bu, dass er wieder aufatmen kann!

source: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_SEQ_03<tab>Bo Bu rejoices to hear that Zo Ga's followers have been served due justice for their misdeeds. Your efforts having instilled the dustman with a measure of courage, perhaps the day when the 789th rises against their oppressors is not so far in the future...
target: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_SEQ_03<tab>Bo Bu ist beeindruckt, wie schnell und effizient du seinen Auftrag ausgeführt hast. Jetzt traut er sich schon eher wieder in die Minen und hofft darauf, bald wieder dort arbeiten zu können anstatt in dem kargen Abbaugebiet des 789. Ordens. Hilf den unterdrückten Kobolden dabei, ihren Traum zu verwirklichen!

source: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_TODO_00<tab>Slay Zo Ga's minions in U'Ghamaro Mines.
target: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_TODO_00<tab>In den U'Ghamaro-Minen Zo Gas Elite-Kobolde besiegen

source: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_TODO_01<tab>Report to 789th Order Dustman Bo Bu.
target: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_TODO_01<tab>Bo Bu erzählen, dass die Luft rein ist

source: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_BOBU_000_000<tab>Zo Ga is not so great─not so high, not so mighty, not so great. No, no, Zo Ga himself is no stronger than me or you─you or I.
target: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_BOBU_000_000<tab>Pfui, pfui, ekelhaft, stinkige Luft aus U'Ghamaro-Minen weht! Die Stollen von Zo Gas Schergen verpestet sind. Dorthin wir uns nicht mehr trauen. Keine Luft wir dort bekommen.

source: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_BOBU_000_001<tab>So why does Zo Ga get his way, you say? An astute question─sharp, keen, astute.
target: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_BOBU_000_001<tab>Die Minen von großem Titan uns geschenkt wurden. Unsere Heimat sind! Dort wir leben wollen!

source: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_BOBU_000_002<tab>Zo Ga has many friends in U'Ghamaro─lackeys, minions, friends. Yes, yes, powerful friends.
target: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_BOBU_000_002<tab>Für frische Luft du dort sorgst, ja? Zo Gas Stinker du beseitigst, ja?

source:
TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_BOBU_000_003<tab>When Zo Ga says, “Dig!” they say, “How deep?”
When Zo Ga says, “Kill Bo Bu!” they say, “How dead?”
TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_BOBU_000_004<tab>Without his friends, Zo Ga will be a shadow of himself─a husk, a shell, a shadow. The 789th will have a fighting chance. Yes, yes, we will!
target: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_BOBU_000_004<tab>... ach ja ... und <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F209D8030202 /var> und <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 06F209D9030202 /var>. Fünf davon du ausschaltest, ja? Egal, welche!

source: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_BOBU_000_005<tab>Without his friends, Zo Ga will be a shadow of himself─a husk, a shell, a shadow. The 789th will have shred of hope. Yes, yes, a fighting chance!
target: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_BOBU_000_005<tab>Igittigitt, noch immer fauliger Gestank aus Stollen weht. Zo Gas Elite-Stinker in U'Ghamaro-Minen du beseitigst und frischen Wind schaffst, ja?

source: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_BOBU_000_010<tab>Somewhere, Zo Ga clenches his fists in rage─anger, fury, rage. Yes, yes, you have done well. Well you have done.
target: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_BOBU_000_010<tab>Ohhh, schnell, schnell du bist! Skaetswys nicht zu viel versprochen hat.

source: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_BOBU_000_011<tab>The revolution begins, begins slowly but surely. Soon, Zo Ga will stand alone─abandoned, adrift, alone─and we will have our revenge. Yes, yes, revenge will be ours!
target: TEXT_BANKOB302_01365_BOBU_000_011<tab>Luft in Stollen jetzt schon viel besser ist. Schon eher wir uns wieder dorthin trauen. Hoffentlich bald wir wieder dort arbeiten und karges Abbaugebiet hinter uns lassen.
